Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.31,0:00:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\N Just Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.51,0:00:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.98,0:00:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.52,0:00:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.63,0:00:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.84,0:00:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.64,0:00:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.92,0:01:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.03,0:01:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.67,0:01:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.37,0:01:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.44,0:01:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒不盡的流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.05,0:01:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙瘋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.08,0:01:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要把一切毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.98,0:01:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾，我不會逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的背後有衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.59,0:01:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.20,0:01:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是…\N這時代不再需要的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.07,0:01:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二十六話\N[燃燒不盡的流星]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.79,0:02:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝入大氣層的運輸機接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的目標明顯是這基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.23,0:02:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是傳聞中的新型機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是MD嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.87,0:02:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.03,0:02:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以要催毀這基地來說\N數目非常少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.14,0:02:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我們不可以輸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.27,0:02:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為[特列斯派]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.61,0:02:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[新星作戰]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是羅姆斐拉財團完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.68,0:02:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙的MD生產線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.15,0:02:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它們降下地球的作戰名稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.09,0:02:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了得到地球上的整體權力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.09,0:02:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊有可能反抗的地域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.20,0:02:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強迫他們歸於財團的支配下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.14,0:03:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在敵人能夠使用雷射砲之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盡量接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.61,0:03:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有那樣才有勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.61,0:03:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體出擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.78,0:03:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衝過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新星作戰\N宇宙好像很喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把麻煩的東西送落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.11,0:04:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了增強兵力支配世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.41,0:04:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們成功開發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.61,0:04:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名為MD的無人機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，關於使用這些MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.79,0:04:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其內部有人提出反對意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.96,0:04:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是OZ統帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪爾麥優侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對羅姆斐拉財團要走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢茍同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古老良好傳統是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.01,0:04:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類的深奧感情構成的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.61,0:04:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我覺得戰鬥是美麗的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會申訴生命是平等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會向逝去的靈魂表示哀掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.99,0:04:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不須要人類的MD的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自動考慮把OZ解體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.86,0:05:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但想保留現有勢力的\N羅姆斐拉財團高層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.03,0:05:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想藉著軟禁特列斯來鎮壓事態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.64,0:05:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N那安排現在令支持特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.61,0:05:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反對引入MD的OZ士兵們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自稱[特列斯派]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.58,0:05:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反抗羅姆斐拉財團的支配制度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.29,0:05:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.39,0:05:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用普通方法果然不能消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.76,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受特列斯特校影響的士兵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,增加了多餘的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茲巴洛夫，繼續增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.00,0:05:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MD派落地球的數量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.37,0:05:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你不用擔心\N宇宙方面很順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新出現的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.11,0:05:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也和駕駛員一起被扣押了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.31,0:05:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在月面基地消滅他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.75,0:06:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈有可能被叛亂份子當作象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.39,0:06:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要從速解決，茲巴洛夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軟禁特列斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只會令時代一直轉壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反抗的人就格殺勿論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.34,0:06:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是最簡單和最可靠的措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.91,0:06:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我殺死你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.77,0:06:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.09,0:07:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茲巴洛夫司令批準\N處決鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.23,0:07:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們再反抗，我們就不留情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.63,0:07:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看來想死在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯派嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉了所有目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.92,0:07:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是遠遠超乎想像的反應速度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續試吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提升模擬水平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.66,0:07:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特蘭特特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡到茲巴洛夫司令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.50,0:07:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令，這個駕駛艙裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.20,0:07:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來果然裝有強化駕駛員腦波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.84,0:08:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提升戰鬥能力的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.31,0:08:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,測試駕駛員顯出相等於
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MD的反應速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.18,0:08:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特蘭特\N你聽不到我的命令嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.62,0:08:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你毀滅鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.69,0:08:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為蕾蒂‧安的叛變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼彈的五名技師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在潛伏於這基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.96,0:08:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別為無聊的事浪費時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這個系統也能用在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.73,0:08:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們OZ的機動戰士上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.47,0:08:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能使用這部鋼彈的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在消除鋼彈這字眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倚靠那種東西做甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.81,0:08:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把鋼彈從宇宙的一切記憶裡洗掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茲巴洛夫司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把一切賭在MD身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎辦?特蘭特特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它解體很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.79,0:08:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但之前，我有數據想記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能和MD...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.13,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對等戰鬥的駕駛員的數據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.44,0:09:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，腦波沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼檢查?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.95,0:09:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正調查飛翼0的駕駛系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.35,0:09:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會給予腦波甚麼影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題，那系統很完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯‧克修里那達因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅姆斐拉財團總部的決定而被軟禁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.63,0:09:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.63,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OZ的軍力現在被一分為二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾蒂‧安中槍倒下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.63,0:09:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生死未卜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.64,0:09:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\N她被當作背叛羅姆斐拉的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪歐‧麥斯威爾和張五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.81,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁OZ內亂成功逃脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩部鋼彈的完成度只有80%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.72,0:09:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，之後只差細微的調較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩人只要一些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.46,0:09:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能把它們完成吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.26,0:10:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦‧巴頓呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨著拜葉特的爆炸下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生還的可能性非常之低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.61,0:10:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不想戰鬥力下降\N但沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.61,0:10:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是現在的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.18,0:10:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.38,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個基地特列斯派的情況吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.92,0:10:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.09,0:10:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我求你們去搜索\N特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.23,0:10:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還可能活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那空域有很多衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.00,0:10:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他…他一定能活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種性格嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.70,0:10:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為士兵有點問題啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.74,0:10:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，雖然擁有那系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.21,0:10:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但鋼彈卻落入敵人手裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它在駕駛艙裝有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令戰鬥的精神波增幅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.38,0:11:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能令駕駛員發揮數倍能力的裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.59,0:11:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對OZ有敵對心是好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.89,0:11:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但駕駛員今次的目的有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為作為士兵還不夠完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以它的能力引致自相殘殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜葉特和麥丘留士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有，加上那部鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.84,0:11:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能一次催毀月面基地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的運動能力和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰術上的想像力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.61,0:11:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透過訓練已經達至完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.68,0:11:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，士兵的精神方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.45,0:11:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們相信還不夠完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.62,0:11:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此才引致今次這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要成為完美的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.06,0:11:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們不能活過MD的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.97,0:11:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類瘋了也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.74,0:11:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於飛翼0的系統你知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.75,0:12:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部份早已完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.15,0:12:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只顧著建造大型能源砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.69,0:12:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連駕駛艙系統也沒注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能源砲還未收回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.33,0:12:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只剩光劍和肩膀的機關砲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.90,0:12:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛，你要戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能把它交給敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.04,0:12:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛，在這場戰爭裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.78,0:12:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪邊是朋友?哪邊是敵人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.62,0:12:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要取自己性命的人和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.62,0:12:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己想打倒的目標就是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.22,0:12:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，如果自己錯了怎辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.43,0:12:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾，我們沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但名為戰爭的時代\N卻有可能變得瘋狂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AB區的閘門被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.21,0:13:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多士兵正前來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特列斯派的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經包圍各位的根據地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會毫不猶豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.99,0:13:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不容分說的\N和曾是戰友的你們戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.22,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不用流無謂的血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全被包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是叫我們出去交易嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.93,0:13:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不能答應\N釋放你們所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.00,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我能保証你們的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.07,0:13:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們先要互相合作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.15,0:13:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來五位博士也在那裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼要求?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.62,0:13:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你們把鋼彈的駕駛員交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想記錄那部鋼彈的戰鬥數據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好像發覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.76,0:13:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對OZ也有魅力的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.86,0:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法，叫駕駛員投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於五位博士的生死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總部的決定毫不留情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.57,0:14:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恐怕無能為力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們活到這年紀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.41,0:14:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是死的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經有心理準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.12,0:14:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先作為人質嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.39,0:14:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早已料到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.40,0:14:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，那種事對希洛不會有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛，有甚麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和他們說開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N讓他和MD的數據戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.02,0:14:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.66,0:15:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常高的水平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.16,0:15:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.67,0:15:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MD以上嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.80,0:15:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有餘力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輸出極限反應速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.57,0:15:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能戰勝MD的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭竟然不須要人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.01,0:15:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛，戰鬥的是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.58,0:15:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類想倚靠機械\N得到戰鬥的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛!錯了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.29,0:15:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這部鋼彈是錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是非常高的戰鬥能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.31,0:15:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的敵人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.58,0:15:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的敵人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.15,0:15:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要取我性命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.65,0:15:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.49,0:16:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!起動系統沒關掉嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.66,0:16:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.37,0:16:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用MD制止他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.64,0:16:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是!那不是希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.06,0:16:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的敵人是要取我性命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.99,0:16:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有玩弄我的性命的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是我的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.67,0:16:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人質不會對他們有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.24,0:16:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那替希洛製造了戰鬥目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.71,0:17:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這宇宙不需要的是OZ和我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.65,0:17:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那系統會搞亂人類思考的平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想利用那系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰勝MD的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.39,0:17:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也已經瘋了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去受死嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.63,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們輸了就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輸給名為戰爭的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特蘭特特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡茲巴洛夫司令要求支援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.04,0:17:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!我怎能報告這次失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特尉!那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停步!你做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.75,0:17:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們也不想死在這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會令他停止攻擊  甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.86,0:17:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的力量能催毀這基地的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.20,0:17:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特洛瓦也說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.50,0:17:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士的駕駛員\N也不行失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只靠排斥別人的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭絕對不會完結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.63,0:18:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個駕駛艙會提升戰鬥能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時，你會有東西失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我因為那個駕駛艙而失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.64,0:18:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我因為那種無聊的機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.00,0:18:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而失去了寶貴的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.01,0:18:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼\N我不想再失去寶貴的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡特爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.35,0:18:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在能清楚看見敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.32,0:18:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你也要做我的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.82,0:18:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就殺死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.32,0:18:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部鋼彈是孤獨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以孤獨作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤獨會失去目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.03,0:18:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能清楚看見我的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這部機動戰士還剩下自爆系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不停止戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.72,0:19:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在此毀滅\N這兩部機動戰士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.69,0:19:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些機動戰士對宇宙來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是最不需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.46,0:19:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且，宇宙有更不需要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙需要鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.77,0:19:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護宇宙，我要戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.00,0:19:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.51,0:19:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙不需要的是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.51,0:19:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.49,0:20:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不可以戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.83,0:20:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不可以戰鬥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.24,0:20:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.63,0:20:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.08,0:20:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是身在地球的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.32,0:20:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.42,0:21:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去地球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球很溫柔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.91,0:21:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又死不了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.84,0:22:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這東西也活下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.95,0:22:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未來是否需要這東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.65,0:22:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就由他們來決定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.59,0:22:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會輸給這種機動戰士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.09,0:22:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.01,0:22:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.01,0:22:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.01,0:22:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.01,0:22:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.51,0:22:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.01,0:23:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.51,0:23:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.01,0:23:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.01,0:23:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.27,0:23:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,次回予告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.67,0:23:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勝利者的交替不斷重覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.44,0:23:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們一直被鬥爭的歷史玩弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.98,0:23:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在戰亂的火炎裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.71,0:23:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希洛等人漫無目的地在流浪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.62,0:23:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在戰爭裡有甚麼得失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.15,0:23:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而現在，望著他們的背影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.99,0:23:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉娜能說甚麼?
